    "biography": "<p>A sentient walking and killing crystal pitcher of Drool-Aid brand sugar-tastic drink mix. The Drool-Aid People are summoned to Terra-Realm from their home dimension of Burgerworld. Once summoned through ritual and incantation, the Drool-Aid Man can be enslaved by the caster and made to do their biddings.</p><p></p><p class=\"p1\">When at half of their starting life total the Drool-Aid Man begins to crack and spill toxic liquid. Anyone in melee combat with them takes 1D4 damage anytime their attack is successful. When the Drool-Aid Man dies it shatters and anyone within 10ft makes an Agility Saving Throw or be hit by shrapnel and toxic liquid. On a failed save they take 2D6 damage. A 10ft radius where the drool-aid man died becomes caustic and if any creature moves in the radius takes 1D6 damage per 5ft of travel.</p>",
    "alignment": "Khaotic",
    "hd": 5,
    "xp": 0,
    "to_the_max_normal": "Punch right to the face knocking out [[1D4]] Teeth, and dealing an additional [[1D6]] damage.",
    "to_the_max_ouch": "FLAVOR BLAST! The Drool-Aid man vomits his insides on the target dissolving skin and intestines leaving nothing but a skeleton. Instant death."
  },
